548
00:19:53.859 --> 00:19:55.820
Hey. hey! Wait up!

549
00:19:55.861 --> 00:19:56.946
[ Sighs ]

550
00:19:56.987 --> 00:19:58.072
What?

551
00:19:58.155 --> 00:19:59.490
Aah!

552
00:19:59.532 --> 00:20:01.200
Schleemypants: Oh. shit!

553
00:19:59.532 --> 00:20:01.200
